subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Novak Djokovic defeated the Australian teenager Bernard Tomic to reach the Wimbledon semifinals, where he will play Jo-Wilfried Tsonga after Tsonga upset Roger Federer.
